profile:
Welcome to From Dark To Light Carpet & Upholstery Care. 

We are two friends reunited in Canada, and we decided to start our own cleaning business. 
Our service is combination of Eco-friendly products, knowledgeable and experience technicians, most updated equipment, strict procedures and love for what we do. 

Cleaning procedures are: vacuuming, pre spraying, agitation, hot water extraction and buffing. Disinfection and scotch guard protection are always an option. 
Donâ€™t let your carpet or upholstery to be a breeding ground for germs and bacteria or allergens. Clean carpets and upholstery make your environment healthier.  

When it comes to pet enzyme decontamination we are experts. We can solve even the most severe pet urine accidents.  

We take a pride in the work we do, and we guarantee you'll love the results of our carpet and upholstery cleaning service!

Our Business Hours: 8:00 am until 9:00 pm, 7 days a week 

Available for Emergency stains and carpet cleaning as well.

*** Covid 19 Update: We will be wearing PPE and practicing social distancing while attending the appointments ***

profile:
Novacovers (Profline Textile Inc.) represents the Italian manufacturer of innovative sofa silpcovers in Canada.
GA.I.CO. s.r.l. is especially known for the production of two way stretch sofa slipcovers made of embossed bi-stretch fabric.
The possible extension both in height and in width of the two way stretch fabric makes our sofa slipcovers perfect for the most different kind of sofas, chairs, armchairs and also for several models of corner sofas.

The quality of our items is internationally recognized and it is guaranteed by careful controls we personally deal with.
The production of our two way stretch slipcovers and sofa slipcovers, in fact, takes place exclusively in our Italian factory.
Since we directly deal with production, we can make exclusive collections.

Since 2001 GA.I.CO. s.r.l. has been specialising in embossed bi-stretch fabrics that are internationally patented.
In 2011 the new brand Paulato By GA.I.CO. Â® was created in order to allow the company to spread all over the world.

The company named Paulato Adriano was born in 1965.
Up to 1979, year in which the company changes location and takes the current name of GA.I.CO. s.r.l., they had been mainly manufacturing fringes and bobbin laces.

Since 2001 GA.I.CO. s.r.l. has been specialising in embossed two way stretch fabrics that are internationally patented.
In 2011 the new brand Paulato by GA.I.CO. Â® was created in order to allow the company to spread all over the world.

Today we are especially known for the production of two way stretch sofa slipcovers made of embossed bi-stretch fabric.
The possible extension both in height and in width of the two way stretch fabric makes our sofa slipcovers perfect for the most different kind of sofas, chairs, armchairs and also for several models of corner sofas.

The quality of our items is internationally recognized and it is guaranteed by careful controls we personally deal with.
The production of our two way stretch slipcovers and sofa slipcovers, in fact, takes place exclusively in our Italian factory.
